(4)	We have relied on Customer Booking Details and Their Pan Card /Aadhar Card Details and Mobile Number Provided by the Client.
(5)	As Client Informed that the unsecured loan is purely unsecured loans and no advance amount received against any booking of Flats / Shops.
(6)	As Client Informed that loan and advances are Loans and Advances.
(7)	ONE OF THE UNIT ESTIMATED SALES PROCEEDS WAS RS 1700000 BUT RS. 2000000 SALES OF AGREEMENT WAS, DONE SO WE HAVE SHOWN RS 2000000 AS COLLECTION AMOUNT FORM 3A.
(8)	ONE OF THE UNIT ESTIMATED SALES PROCEEDS WAS RS 1500000 BUT RS. 1700000 SALES OF AGREEMENT WAS, DONE SO WE HAVE SHOWN RS 1700000 AS COLLECTION AMOUNT FORM 3A.
(9)	ONE OF THE UNIT ESTIMATED SALES PROCEEDS WAS RS 1700000 BUT RS. 1250000 SALES OF AGREEMENT WAS, DONE SO WE HAVE SHOWN RS 1250000 AS COLLECTION AMOUNT FORM 3A.

(10)	ONE UNIT MAINTEANACE DEPOSIT BY MISTAKE TRANSFERRED IN RERA ACCOUNT WHICH IS NOT CONSIDRED THE SAME AND WHICH WILL BE REPAID FROM CURRENT ACCOUNT.

(11)	Mortgaged Loan Taken from kadi Nagrik Sahkari Bank against 98 units mortgaged out of which NOC Received from bank we have removed from the Mortgaged Created from that units in FORM NO. 3A  and as per the renewal agreement  Mortgage Loan Limit was Rs. 4,10,00,000/-  due to that  8 Unbooked shops, 3 booked units and 17 unbooked  units so total 28 units were mortgaged with the Bank.

(12)	 Total Estimated Project Cost of Construction was Rs. 24,00,00,000/- while actual incurred and paid was RS.26,35,96,230/-  which is exceeding the Estimated Cost of Constructions. Form no. 02 was RS 24,00,00,000/- Due not able to update the estimated cost of project as the projects is Completed.

(13)	 Total Estimated Cost of Project was RS. 28,59,53.625 While actual incurred and paid was RS. 31,23,79,123/- which is exceeding the Total Estimated Cost of Project.
 
(14)	 Bu Received on 01/07/2022. 
15  Estimated Interest was Rs. 20610000 while actual interest expenses was RS. 16,149,390 this is due to early payment of loan and early closer of project.
